data.description: If you're looking for charm, a functional floor plan, NON cookie cutter, large yard & still want it to feel like new construction.... this is the home for you! Home was beautifully renovated in 2022 - all new: plumbing, hvac, roof, kitchen appliances, electrical, windows, lighting, bathrooms. There is also a large mudroom that is perfectly located in the back of the home that way you (or pets) have somewhere to tidy up after enjoying your spacious yard! Owner loves sitting outside on the covered patio. Conveniently located within minutes from shopping, restaurants and schools. Come take a tour on this fantastic unique home - USDA eligible!
